                             angular
                                                                  bank app in angular
                                                                  front end:angular
                                                                  back end: nodejs(express)
                                                                  database:mongodb

        basic commands
 
1.create a projectn - ng new projectname
2.create a component - ng g c componentname
3.run - ng serve -o


{{html--view}}
{{ts-component--logic}}

###data binding ----to share data inside component

1.one way data binding   (ts to html or html to ts)
       a)component to view
               a1)string interpolation-{{ex}}
               a2)property binding -[atribute name]='property'
        b) view to component
               b1)event binding-(event_name)="function name" 
               b2)event binding using $event -  (event_name)="function name($event)"  
                
               b3)event binding using template referecing variable-#variable_name
2. two way binding
data share in both direction...html to ts/// ts to html
ngmodel(library)-import from forms module
